{"tid":764971,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人硬係同文職扯唔上關係","createTime":"2018-08-02T11:30:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-03T03:39:27.000Z","uid":196942,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"58026ae8067dee80e3db1171cdc239a27901c94e","tid":764971,"uid":196942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T11:30:02.000Z","msg":"未出嚟做野之前 我一直都以為自己未來會做死文職<br />\n我個性格宅宅地 自己一個塞埋一二邊對住部電腦禁禁禁 電話叉下電又一日 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點知出到嚟做野 第一次做既文員工partime順利番左兩個月 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之後就開始衰啦<br />\n一份做左第4日半就叫我拎錢走人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幾日嚟都係叫我痴下野寫下野<br />\n第二份做左三日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 收左工無啦啦比人通知叫我唔洗再番 我問點解 我無啦啦比人炒都想知點死法嫁嘛 老細話冇原因 就覺得唔啱 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n自問我又冇玩電話 佢要我做既野都做齊哂 同文職總係有種水溝油既感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 而家番緊服務業 都成幾年相安無事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c65c300012cd2538a9b85c049df050ca11b47d8","tid":764971,"uid":186163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T12:02:58.000Z","msg":"咁似我既<br />\n歡迎起我底<br />\n等炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb67503abfe89c15f3691c0364fabb613b17d277","tid":764971,"uid":102179,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T12:16:27.000Z","msg":"服務業係俾狗做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5022a0f4c42a03ff88ea4594349b815337f20994","tid":764971,"uid":12618,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T12:39:05.000Z","msg":"做極都係文職<br />\n太舒服轉唔到工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd10c07f61ff0ec88cb70af43d12dedc34e00e3a","tid":764971,"uid":196942,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T13:15:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>服務業係俾狗做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但我真係寧願好忙都唔想成日坐係同一個位係度對文件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唔通我真係天生狗命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0072037e9707b7c995c6799cdee16119fd36e5eb","tid":764971,"uid":161144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd10c07f61ff0ec88cb70af43d12dedc34e00e3a","tid":764971,"uid":196942,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T13:15:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>服務業係俾狗做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但我真係寧願好忙都唔想成日坐係同一個位係度對文件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唔通我真係天生狗命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T03:39:27.000Z","msg":"天生狗命+1"}]}